    "id": "xc-3503",
    "sport": "xc",
    "date": "2020-11-10",
    "title": "Kyle Woods Finishes 61st at State Meet",
    "categories": [
      "Boys Meet Results",
      "Honors"
    ],
    "gender": "boys",
    "body": "This past weekend Kyle Woods ran 16:30.7 and finished 61st out of 177 runners at the OHSAA Boys Division 1 State Championship.  Kyle did a great job moving up throughout the race.  He went from 92nd at the 1 mile mark, to 76th at the 2 mile mark before finishing 61st. He also earned Academic All-Ohio due to his outstanding GPA.  Kyle finished up an outstanding junior season and will look to move up even more and become an All-Ohioan. I know he wants the team with him there next year!\n\n[Full Results](http://www.finishtimingresults.com/2020/11-07-OHSAA/)\n\nhttps://youtu.be/7J6MqOviYZs",
