    "body": "This past weekend the boys and girls finished 6th and 8th overall respectively at the Stark County Championships hosted at GlenOak High School.  The boys team was lead by Kyle Woods (11th), Connor Reed (15th), Alex Hill (25th), Cooper Reed (41st), and James Wayman (63rd) in scoring.  The girls were lead in scoring by Emily Beck (9th), Sheldyn Daugherty (39th), Bella Troyer (52nd), Reilly Kreger (58th), and Macey Foss (65th).\n\n[Full Results](https://www.baumspage.com/cc/ccevent.php?peventid=22&table=C)\n\nNew PRs were set by:\n\n- Kyle Woods\n\n- Connor Reed\n\n- Alex Hill\n\n- Cooper Reed\n\n- Nathan Singo\n\n- Joe Backus\n\n- Riley Hostetler\n\n- Hayden Giaque\n\n- Evan Creaturo\n\n- Emily Beck\n\n- Bella Troyer\n\n- Audrey Morgan\n\n- Millie Stangelo\n\n- Jocelyn Wright\n\n- Kathryn Shoaff\n\n- Grace Harper",
