    "gender": "boys",
    "body": "The boys cross country team finished 7th place out of 27 schools at the Legends Meet on Saturday at the Trumbull County Fairgrounds.  The team was lead in scoring by Devin Halter, Kyle Woods, Justin Zapotoczny, Dominic Carosielli, and Alex Hill.  The team had many personal bests recorded on the day.  In addition to personal bests out of Kyle, Justin, Dominic, and Alex the team also had personal bests run by Cooper Reed, James Wayman, Spencer Huntsman, Austin Hammock, Owen Rair, Liam Morris, Nathan Singo, and Evan Creaturo.\n\nThe boys and girls teams will compete Saturday at Jackson Middle School at the Federal League Championships at 9:00am.\n\n[Results](https://www.baumspage.com/cc/ccevent.php?peventid=44&table=C)",
