    "date": "2019-08-26",
    "title": "Boys Finish Runner-Up at Sandusky Panther Run to Fun",
    "categories": [
      "Boys Meet Results"
    ],
    "gender": "boys",
    "body": "The boys cross country team opened up their season with a runner-up finish at the Sandusky Panther Run to Fun Invitational on Saturday. The team pulled out the 2nd place finish with some excellent finishing kicks edging Sylvania Southview by 4 points. The team scorers were Devin Halter - 3rd, Brandon Williams - 12th, Nick Forchione - 24th, Kyle Woods - 25th, and Justin Zapotoczny - 32nd in the 266 person race. It was a great day overall for the team followed by some thrilling rides at Cedar Point.  The team will race again this Saturday at the Marlington Invitational.\n\n[Results](https://www.baumspage.com/cc/smcc/2019/Boys%20HS%20Division%20I.pdf)",
