    "sport": "xc",
    "date": "2017-10-10",
    "title": "Federal League Meet Information - Spectator Charge",
    "categories": [
      "Uncategorized"
    ],
    "gender": "both",
    "body": "**Date:**​ Saturday October 14th, 2017\n\n**Location:​** Jackson Middle School - 7355 Mudbrook St NW Massillon, Ohio\n\n**Parking​:** Buses will drop of runners near the main entrance to JMMS and proceed to park at Sauder Elementary which is on the West side of the Football Stadium. Spectator parking will also be located on the West Side of the school where you park for football games. People will be able to cut through the football stadium to access the entrance onto the cross country course.\n\n**Tickets:** ***Adults - $7  Students - $4***\n\n**Schedule:​**\n\n1:00 pm Girls Middle School\n1:30 pm Boys Middle School\n2:00 Boys Varsity\n2:30 Girls Varsity\n3:10 Boys JV\n3:50 Girls JV\n4:30 Coaches Meeting",
    "images": [],
    "archived": true
