    "body": "The Boys  team finished 3rd out of 16 teams at the Pat Ritchie Invitational on Saturday at Walsh Jesuit. The team was lead by Joey Fedor, Jason Lacourt, Jacob Cronk, Eliott Kamerer, and Everett Ewing in scoring.\n\nThe Girls  finished 6th out of 14 teams, without their number 1 and 2 runners. Laura Genetin lead the way with a 12th place finish, followed by Elaine Bast, Grace Volpe, Katie Williams and Hannah Groff.\n\nThe boys race at Boardman this weekend and the girls run next in two weeks at the Strongsville Invitational.\n\n[Results](http://www.baumspage.com/cc/ccevent.php?peventid=6&table=C)",
