    "categories": [
      "Honors"
    ],
    "gender": "both",
    "body": "Perry's Division 1 defending state champion pole vaulter, Lucas Kelley, is featured in the latest issue of The Score Magazine.  As stated by the twitter account [@TheScoreStark](https://twitter.com/TheScoreStark), \"The Score is Stark County’s sports digest. On newsstands quarterly, the glossy, 68-page magazine features articles on area athletes, teams, coaches and more.\"\n\nPick up your copy today!\n\nhttps://twitter.com/mpopovichREP/status/578998160703533056",
