    "date": "2014-08-18",
    "title": "Girls Open Up Season 13th Place Finish at OHSAA Early Season Invite",
    "categories": [
      "Featured",
      "Girls Meet Results"
    ],
    "gender": "girls",
    "body": "The Girls Cross Country team opened up their 2014 season with a 13th place finish at the OHSAA Early Season Invitational last Saturday.  The race was held at National Trail Raceway in Hebron which is the same course the State Meet is held at.  The team's scorers were Carlie Perretta, Madelyn Bartolone, Josey Lacourt, Lexi Echelberry, and Sydnee Fenn.  The girls race this week again at the GlenOak Golden Eagle Invitational.\n\n[Individual Results](http://timerhub.com/getHytResults.php?page=finishtimingresults.com/2014/08-16-OHSAA/130817F001.htm)\n[Team Scores](http://timerhub.com/getHytResults.php?page=finishtimingresults.com/2014/08-16-OHSAA/130817F001C.htm)",
