    "categories": [
      "Boys Meet Results",
      "Featured",
      "Girls Meet Results",
      "Results"
    ],
    "gender": "both",
    "body": "Both teams lost at GlenOak last night.  The boys lost 12-125 and the girls fell 28-109.  Lucas Kelley set a stadium record in pole vault at 15'1\" to win.  Tristan Williams also won the 300 meter hurdles in a season best time of 41.43.  Dom Labriola finished 3rd in both shot put and discus.  On the girls side,  Charliee Strickland had three 2nd place finishes.  Others who scored were Ashley Cilona, Alexa Carpenter, Carlie Perretta, Lia Millin, Autumn Greco, Hannah Volpe, Marrissa Briggs, Lexi Echelberry, and Kylie Church.\n\n[Boys Results](http://perrylocal.org/track/files/2009/10/2014BoysVsGlenOak.pdf)\n[Girls Results](http://perrylocal.org/track/files/2009/10/2014GirlsVsGlenOak.pdf)",
