    "body": "The girls cross country team finished runner-up at the 2013 Stark County Championships.  Lina Partridge (11th) lead the way for the Panthers followed by Taylor Wilson(13th), Sydnee Fenn(17th), Carlie Perretta(21st), and Kylie Church(26th).  The boys team finished 5th overall and were lead by Tristan Williams(7th), Mitchell Paxton(27th), Joe Volpe(41st), Alex Ryan(48th), and Colton Luxenburg(60th).  The boys will race again at Stow this week while the girls have an off week.\n\n[Full Results](http://www.baumspage.com/cc/ccevent.php?peventid=183&table=C)",
