    "body": "The Boys Cross Country team finished 3rd out of 46 teams on Saturday at the Slippery Rock Invitational.  The team brought home the Runner-Up plaque in the AAA division falling to only Mt. Lebanon.  The team was lead by medal placing finishers in Tristan Williams, Alex Ryan, and Joe Volpe.  Mitchell Paxton and Johnny Stevenson rounded out the scoring for the boys.\n\nDue to a bad accident on I-80 the girls team arrived right as their race was starting so they ran in the JV/Open race.  This race was a combined boys and girls race which gave the girls plenty of competition to run fast times on a tough course.\n\n[Full Results](http://runhigh.com/2013RESULTS/R091413AK.html)",
