    "gender": "both",
    "body": "The girls track team finished 5th overall at the Jackson Twilight Meet on Friday night.  Hannah Luke won the 200 meter dash and anchored the 4x200 and 4x400 meter relay teams to wins.  Joining her on the relays were: Charliee Strickland, Jackie Genetin, and Mikayla Dearing.  The boys finished 13th overall and got a winning performance out of Tristan Williams in the 300 meter hurdles in a season best performance of 40.28.  Athletes who scored in the meet are listed below:\n\n- Hannah Luke - 1st in the 200m\n\n- Girls 4x200 team (Charliee Strickland, Jackie Genetin, Mikayla Dearin, Hannah Luke) - 1st\n\n- Girls 4x400 team (Charliee Strickland, Jackie Genetin, Mikayla Dearin, Hannah Luke) - 1st\n\n- Tristan Williams - 1st in the 300m hurdles\n\n- Mikayla Dearing - 3rd in the 400m\n\n- Boys 4x400 team (Devin Myers, Zach James, Alex Colucy, Tristan Williams) - 3rd\n\n- JoJo Tayse - 4th in discus and 7th in shot put\n\n- Marrissa Knop - 4th in shot put\n\n- Girls 4x800 team (Becca Backus, Taylor Wilson, Jackie Genetin, Lia Millian) - 4th\n\n- Anna Oprisch - 5th in shot put\n\n- Charliee Strickland - 6th in the 400m\n\n- Lia Millin - 6th in the 300m hurldes\n\n- Carlie Perretta - 7th in the 1600m\n\n- Boys 4x800 team (Tristan Williams, Zach James, Josh White, Mitchell Paxton) - 8th\n\n[Full Results](http://www.baumspage.com/track/massjackson/2013/Final%20Results_d_Scores%202013.pdf)",
