    "gender": "both",
    "body": "The Girls Track Team defeated Jackson tonight 71-66.  The girls had winning performances out of Marissa Knop, Anna Oprisch, Indy Clark, Hannah Luke, Charliee Strickland, Jackie Genetin, Mikayla Dearing, and Lia Millin.\n\nThe boys track team lost to Jackson 56-81.  The team got wins out of Andrew Vincent, JoJo Tayse, Braxton Berry, Brandon Peters, J-Vonne Humphreys, Dustin DiRocco, Ali Attar, Devin Meyers, Zach James, Alex Colucy, and Tristan Williams.\n\nThe varsity competes again Friday at the Jackson Twilight Invitational.\n\n[Girls Results](http://perrylocal.org/track/files/2013/05/2013PerryJacksonGirls.pdf)\n[Boys Results](http://perrylocal.org/track/files/2013/05/2013PerryJacksonBoys.pdf)",
