    "body": "The Boys Track Team finished 7th at the Boys Only Walsh Warrior Relay Meet on Saturday.  Top placing relays for the boys were the 4x200 (Braxton Berry, Alex Colucy, Danny Williams, Jamie Norris) and 4x100 (J'Vonne Humphreys, Dustin DiRocco, Berry, Ali Attar) which both took 3rd place. 4th Place finishers included: Tristan Williams in the 300m hurdles, 4x800 (T.Williams, Mitchell Paxton, Josh White, Zach James), and the Shot Put Relay (JoJo Tayse, Dom Labriola, Ben Kintz).\n\nThe teams do not compete again until this Saturday at Perry for the 2013 Stark County Championships.\n\n[Full Results](http://www.baumspage.com/track/walshjesuit/2013/Results%202013.htm)",
