    "body": "The girls and boys track teams both opened their season up with losses to GlenOak.  The girls fell by a score of 55-82 and the boys 47-90.  Winning events for the girls were: Marissa Knop, Hannah Luke, Becca Backus, Jackie Genetin, and Mikayla Dearing.  Others who scored for the girls were: Anna Oprisch, Summer Gillard, Marissa Briggs, Lina Partridge, and Charliee Strickland.  JoJo Tayse, Tristan Williams, Jamie Norris, Bryce Williams, Andrew Vincent, Zach James, Mitchell Paxton, and Zach Spencer won events for the boys.  Others who scored for the boys were Lucas Kelley and Ali Attar.\n\nThe varsity girls race Friday at Salem and the boys Saturday at East Palestine.  The full team will be back in action at Hoover on Tuesday.\n\n[Girls Results](http://perrylocal.org/track/files/2013/04/GlenOakPerryGirls2013.pdf)\n[Boys Results](http://perrylocal.org/track/files/2013/04/GlenOakPerryBoys2013.pdf)",
