    "date": "2012-10-01",
    "title": "Girls Finish 4th, Boys 8th at Stark County Championship",
    "categories": [
      "Boys Meet Results",
      "Featured",
      "Girls Meet Results",
      "Middle School Results"
    ],
    "gender": "both",
    "body": "The Girls Cross Country finished 4th out of 16 teams at the Stark County Championships on Saturday.  The team was lead by **Sydnee Fenn**'s 21st place finish and was followed closely by the pack of **Taylor Wilson**, **Lina Partridge**, **Carlie Perretta**, and **Becca Backus**.  The boys team finished 8th place out of 20 teams and were lead by **Joe Volpe** and **Tristan Williams** who finished 21st and 23rd respectively.  The others to score for the boys were **Mitchell Paxton**, **Colton Luxenburg**, and **Alex Ryan**.  The girls middle school team finished 5th and the boys team finished 7th.  The teams will compete at the Stow Invitational Saturday.\n\n[Full Results](http://www.baumspage.com/cc/ccevent.php?peventid=244&table=C)",
    "images": [],
    "archived": true
