    "categories": [
      "Boys Meet Results"
    ],
    "gender": "boys",
    "body": "The Boys Team competed at the Walsh Warrior Relays Saturday at Walsh Jesuit High School and finished 7th overall.  The team's top performances were in the **4x1600** (Matt Mizer, Aaron Dunn, Seth Kurzen, Matt Thiessen) , the **Distance Medley Relay** (Dunn, Tyler Weisburn, Mizer, David Kamerer), and the **Shot Put Relay** (Giovanni Myers, Ryan Dice, Justin Judd) which all finished 2nd place.  The **4x400** (Tristan Williams, Mizer, Weisburn, Nick Williams) and **High Jump Relay** (Trevor Clere, Skyler Jackson,  Tyler Weston) each finished 3rd.\n\n[Full Results](http://www.baumspage.com/track/walshjesuit/2012/2012%20Results.htm)",
