    "gender": "both",
    "body": "The boys and girls track teams traveled to Lake tonight and both teams came away with victories.  The boys won 98-39 and the girls 79-58.  Winning events for the boys were: Tyler Weisburn, Matt Mizer, David Kamerer, Nick Williams, Brenton Neira, Devin Myers, Jake West, Dustin DiRocco, Aaron Dunn, Tristan Williams, Matt Thiessen, Tyler Weston, Khyler Fields, Andrew Vincent, JoJo Tayse, and Doug Mayes.\n\nWinning events for the girls were: Hailey Floom, Kylie Church, Becca Backus, Jackie Genetin, Charliee Strickland, Marissa Briggs, Mikayla Deering, Indy Clark, Summer Gillard, and Danielle Fisher.\n\nThe boys team will compete Saturday at the Walsh Warrior Relays and the girls will be back in action along with them next Tuesday at home against McKinley.\n\n[Boys Results](http://perrylocal.org/track/files/2012/04/2012PerryBoysLake.pdf)\n[Girls Results](http://perrylocal.org/track/files/2012/04/2012PerryGirlsLake.pdf)",
