    "date": "2012-03-15",
    "title": "Team Qualifies in 6 Events to Indoor State Meet",
    "categories": [
      "Featured",
      "Honors"
    ],
    "gender": "both",
    "body": "The Indoor Track Teams have qualified to the Indoor State Meet Saturday at the University of Akron by being ranked in the top 16 in the state this season:\n\n- Hannah Luke - 60m dash\n\n- Hannah Luke - 200m dash\n\n- Girls 4 x 400m Relay of Hailey Floom, Jackie Genetin,  Charliee Strickland, and Mikayla Dearing\n\n- Trevor Clere - Boys High Jump\n\n- Doug Mayes - Boys Shot Put\n\n- Doug Mayes - Boys Weight Throw\n\nTickets are $8 at the door and the schedule for the meet and more information can be found below:\n\n[http://www.oatccc.com/track/StateIndoorChampionships_MeetSchedule_2012.pdf](http://www.oatccc.com/track/StateIndoorChampionships_MeetSchedule_2012.pdf)\n[http://www.oatccc.com/track/OATCCCStateChampionships/RegistrationWindow.html](http://www.oatccc.com/track/OATCCCStateChampionships/RegistrationWindow.html)",
