    "id": "track-3391",
    "sport": "track",
    "date": "2012-02-06",
    "title": "5 Individual Winners and 2 Relay Winners at Mount Union Indoor Meet",
    "categories": [
      "Boys Meet Results",
      "Featured",
      "Girls Meet Results"
    ],
    "gender": "both",
    "body": "The Panther Indoor Track Team had several good performances at the Mount Union High School Indoor Open yesterday.  There were 5 individual event winners which consisted of Trevor Clere (high jump), Matt Mizer (1600m), Hannah Luke (60m), Hailey Floom (400m), and Skyler Jackson (triple jump). Skyler's 37 feet 4.5 inch Triple Jump is a new school record.  The 4x400 relay teams: David Kamerer, Tyler Weisburn, Danny Tilton and Tristan Williams and Hailey Floom, Jackie Genetin, Meredith Mann, and Charliee Strickland also won.  Others who competed well in scoring good marks on the day were Seth Kurzen, Tyler Weston and Lia Millin",
