    "body": "The Stark County Cross Country Coaches Association held their post season awards meeting last night at Walsh University.  Perry Cross Country was well represented on the All-County teams and Senior All-Star race.\n\n**1st Team All-County - Girls - **Sydnee Fenn** - Boys - **Aaron Dunn, Matt Thiessen\n\n**2nd Team All-County - Girls - **Jackie Genetin, Hailey Floom, Taylor Wilson** - Boys - **Drew Tormasi, Seth Kurzen\n\n**Honorable Mention All-County - Girls - **Carlie Perretta** - Boys - **Tristan Williams\n\n**Stark County Senior All-Star Selections**: Hailey Floom**, **Aaron Dunn, Matt Thiessen, Seth Kurzen, David Kamerer",
