    "gender": "both",
    "body": "Perry Cross Country runners who will not be competing on Saturday at Boardman for the Regional Championship competed at the Walsh Warrior Classic Invitational on Monday.  It was a very wet and muddy course that slowed times down by quite a bit.  Races were divided amongst Freshmen/Sophomores and Juniors/Seniors for both the boys and the girls.  The races were not scored but there were individuals who received awards for finishing in the top 25 amongst their grades.  Results of just Perry runners  are listed below\n\n**Boys Results**\n\n**Name**\n**Race**\n**Time**\n**Place**\n\nDrew Tormasi\nJr/Sr\n18:59\n1st\n\nTristan Williams\nFr/So\n19:16\n2nd\n\nDavid Kamerer\nJr/Sr\n19:27\n6th\n\nMitchell Paxton\nFr/So\n19:39\n5th\n\nMatt Mizer\nJr/Sr\n20:19\n21st\n\nTyler Weisburn\nJr/Sr\n20:27\n22nd\n\nColton Luxenburg\nFr/So\n20:33\n24th\n\nAdam Tyler\nFr/So\n20:40\n26th\n\nZach James\nJr/Sr\n20:46\n31st\n\nWinston Davis\nFr/So\n21:12\n41st\n\nDan Quinn\nJr/Sr\n21:29\n46th\n\nJoe Volpe\nFr/So\n21:37\n57th\n\nTim Watkins\nJr/Sr\n21:52\n54th\n\nEric Oster\nFr/So\n21:56\n66th\n\nBrian Theis\nJr/Sr\n22:24\n63rd\n\nAlex Ryan\nFr/So\n22:33\n74th\n\nCal Curtin\nJr/Sr\n22:36\n64th\n\n**\nGirls Results**\n\n**Name**\n**Race**\n**Time**\n\nSummer Gillard\nJr/Sr\n24:13\n\nKelsey Cobb\nFr/So\n24:37\n\nErica Curtin\nFr/So\n25:07\n\nTrisha Barnett\nFr/So\n25:25\n\nMeredith Mann\nJr/Sr\n25:45\n\nSara Keane\nFr/So\n26:56\n\nAnna Haas\nJr/Sr\n27:18\n\nJulie Brown\nJr/Sr\n27:31\n\nCassie Mann\nFr/So\n29:31\n\nHailea Briggs\nJr/Sr\n31:03",
