    "body": "The Perry 5th and 6th Grade Running Club ran a one mile race Thursday with the high school cross country teams.  There were many great performances by these young runners on a great day to run. \n\nResults are listed below.  Note: not everyone turned in their card with their name on it.\n\n**Name**\n**Time**\n\nRebekah Brown\n6:11\n\nAdrina Hufstetler\n6:16\n\nDavid Wertz\n6:29\n\nKasey Centeno\n6:32\n\nNatalie Wilson\n6:36\n\nJacob Cronk\n6:41\n\nGreg Walter\n6:47\n\nJosey LaCourt\n6:58\n\nMegan Fehlman\n7:07\n\nGunner McCollins\n7:14\n\nBill Williams\n7:27\n\nPeyton Clarke\n7:34\n\nKevin Echelberry\n7:35\n\nHannah Flagg\n7:45\n\n7:48\n\nElliott Kamerer\n7:49\n\n7:58\n\n7:59\n\nJenna Molinari\n8:08\n\nMadison Violand\n8:10\n\n8:24\n\nAlec Conversino\n8:25\n\nKyndel Fenn\n8:32\n\nTristan Rohr\n8:32\n\nMakaya Young\n8:59\n\n9:01\n\n9:19\n\n9:27\n\nHallie Kesegich\n9:34\n\nT.J. Ochsenfeld\n9:59\n\n10:04\n\n10:17\n\n10:37\n\nBraedy Luxenburg\n10:42\n\n11:04",
