    "date": "2011-04-05",
    "title": "Boys and Girls Both Beat Lake",
    "categories": [
      "Boys Meet Results",
      "Featured",
      "Girls Meet Results",
      "Results"
    ],
    "gender": "both",
    "body": "The Boys Track Team beat Lake 91-46 and the Girls Team won 84-53.  Winning events for boys were: Doug Mayes, Matt Thiessen, Tyler Weisburn, Aaron Dunn, Aaron White, Bodhi Martin, Tony Magnacca, Joey DiCicco, McKinley Lancaster, Drew Tormasi, Marcus Peffer, and D.J. Marlatt.  Winning events for the girls were: Kyrra Eaton, Marissa Knop, Marlene Masalko, Hailey Floom, Shelby Logan, Becca Backus, Tara Rodgers, Michelle Genetin, Stacy Cameron, Jackie Genetin, Hannah Luke, and Rebecca Paxton.\n\nThe teams will be in action again this Saturday at the Lexington Invitational.\n\n[Boys Results](http://perrylocal.org/track/files/2011/04/PerryBoysVsLake.pdf)\n[Girls Results](http://perrylocal.org/track/files/2011/04/PerryGirlsVsLake.pdf)",
