    "id": "track-2790",
    "sport": "track",
    "date": "2011-04-04",
    "title": "Alumni Update: Ty Griffin and LePear Smith Run Well",
    "categories": [
      "Alumni",
      "Featured"
    ],
    "gender": "both",
    "body": "**Ty Griffin** won both the 800 meter run and the 4x800 relay in the OAC Gold Meet at Mount Union on Saturday. ** LePear Smith** improved his 110 meter high hurdle time to 15.19 in taking 3rd at Walsh.  Others who competed this past weekend are listed below.\n\n**Athlete**\n**College**\n**Events**\n**Results/Location**\n\nTy Griffin ('07)\nMount Union\n800m-1:58.67-1st, 4x800-1st\n[Results - Mount Union](http://athletics.mountunion.edu/sports/mtrack/2010-11/files/Results.htm)\n\nDan Harsh (’08)\nWalsh\nHJ-5-10.75, 200m-24.22\n[Results - Walsh](http://www.walsh.edu/uploads/TrackResults-13752.htm)\n\nKaylie Snyder ('09)\nAshland\n1500m-5:10.91, 3000m-11:20.47\n[Results - Akron](http://www.gozips.com/downloads2/409927.htm?ATCLID=205128654&SPSID=47088&SPID=4310&DB_OEM_ID=10800)\n\nBrandon Wollenberg  (’09)\nWalsh\n3000m-9:44.30\n[Results - Walsh](http://www.walsh.edu/uploads/TrackResults-13752.htm)\n\nJustin Eddy (’10)\nWalsh\n3000m-9:06.60\n[Results - Walsh](http://www.walsh.edu/uploads/TrackResults-13752.htm)\n\nLePear Smith (’10)\nMalone\n110h-15.19-3rd, 100m-11.41-2nd\n200m-23.84-3rd\n[Results - Walsh](http://www.walsh.edu/uploads/TrackResults-13752.htm)\n\nCorey Williams ('10)\nCase Western\n5000m-16:58.60\n[Results - Depauw](http://www.walsh.edu/uploads/TrackResults-13752.htm)",
