    "body": "We had 7 alumni athletes compete this past weekend.  Results are listed below:\n\n**Athlete**\n**College**\n**Events**\n**Results/Location**\n\nDan Harsh ('08)\nWalsh\nHigh Jump-5-11, Long Jump-19-7\n[Results](http://oh.milesplit.com/meets/84202/results/147796) - Geneva\n\nElizabeth Flinner ('09)\nBall State\nWeight Throw-35-4\n[Results](http://ballstatesports.com/downloads2/398741.htm?ATCLID=205086142&SPSID=62084&SPID=6775&DB_LANG=C&DB_OEM_ID=14200) - IWU\n\nKaylan Lemon ('09)\nBaldwin-Wallace\n4x200-2nd, 4x400-3rd, 55m-7.55\n[Results](http://www.capital.edu/32206.html) - OAC Relays\n\nKaylie Snyder ('09)\nAshland\nMile-5:41.06, 3000m-11:20.18\n[Results](http://athletics.findlay.edu/sports/extrainfo/4409.htm) - Findlay\n\nJustin Eddy ('10)\nWalsh\n3000m-9:03.64\n[Results](http://oh.milesplit.com/meets/84202/results/147796) - Geneva\n\nTori Machan ('10)\nMount Union\n5000m-20:42.49\n[Results](http://www.capital.edu/32206.html) - OAC Relays\n\nCorey Williams ('10)\nCase Western\nMile-4:54.61, 800m-2:21.22\n[Results](http://www.case.edu/athletics/varsity/sports_men/trackfield/stats/2010-11/Case%20Results%20Spartans%20-%20Tartans.htm) - CWRU-CMU Dual",
