    "gender": "girls",
    "body": "The girls' cross country ran at the Stow Invitational on  Saturday, taking 3rd overall in the large school division.  Stacy Cameron and  Jackie Genetin lead the team with 10th and 12th place finishes respectively.   Also running well for the team were Becca Backus, Hailey Floom and Tara  Rodgers.  The girls compete in the Federal League Championship this Saturday.",
