    "body": "****\n\nCongratulations to the Boy's Cross Country Team for winning the inaugural  running of the Cedar Point Cross Country Invitational in Sandusky this past  Saturday.  The team was led by senior Justin Eddy, who placed 2nd overall,  followed by a very strong pack consisting of Chase Daniels (3rd), Aaron White  (4th), Corey Williams (5th), Cody Sundley (11th), Nick DiGiulio (15th), and  Kevin McDougal (16th).  The team will be in action again this Saturday at the  Avon Lake Invitational.",
