    "body": "Congratulations to the Boy's Cross Country Team for winning the  District Championship on Saturday.  Leading the way for the team, and  impressively all finishing as Individual Qualifiers, were Josh Tormasi, Brandon  Wollenberg, Justin Eddy, and Shane Gillard.  Others contributing to the Team  Title and running outstanding races were Cody Sundley, Kevin McDougal, Jon  Melnichenko, Chase Daniels, Nick DiGiulio and Corey Williams.  The Team will be  running again this Saturday at GlenOak in the Regional Championship Meet.",
