    "body": "In Boy's Cross Country action this past Saturday, Josh Tormasi  won his first ever elite level cross country invitational race, leading the team  to 2nd place out of 18 teams.  Others contributing to the teams strong 2nd place  finish were Justin Eddy, Brandon Wollenberg, Jon Melnichenko, Shane Gillard,  Kevin McDougal and Cody Sundley.  Others running personal best races were Corey  Williams, Mike McBurney, Chase Daniels, Nathan Clapper, David Kamerer, Aaron  Dunn, Tyler Weisburn, Jake Miller, Matt Mizer, Seth Kurzen, Alec Blend, and  Charlie Jeffreys.\n\nThe team will be in action again this Saturday at the  Boardman Invitational.",
