    "gender": "boys",
    "body": "The boys team finished 7th at GlenOak minus the top 3 runners  (Josh Tormasi, Brandon Wollenberg, and Justin Eddy) who were off for the  weekend.  A lot of new guys got their first crack at a varsity race and  Kevin McDougal came through with a 21 second personal best to finish as the  number 2 runner on the team.  In the open race personal bests were run by  Mike McBurney, David Kamerer, Aaron Dunn, Matt Mizer, Tyler Weisburn, Tyler  Yoder, Seth Kurzen, Jake Miller, Alec Blend, and Charlie Jeffreys.\n\nThe team will be at full strength in action tomorrow at Avon  Lake.  The varsity will run at 9:00 AM followed by the JV at 10:00 and then  the open at 12:00.",
