    "body": "The boy's cross country team placed 5th this past Saturday at  the Midwest Meet of Champions. Leading the team was junior, Brandon Wollenberg.  Others contributing to the 5th place finish were Josh Tormasi, Matt Welch,  Justin Eddy, Ryan Oster, Shane Gillard, and Cody Sundley. The team will be in  action again this Saturday at the Boardman Invitational.  Personal bests  were recorded by Brandon Wollenberg, Justin Eddy, Ryan Oster, Shane Gillard, and  Cody Sundley during this race.\n\nAlso the JV team competed in the varsity race at the Wooster  Invitational and finished 4th overall.  Jon Melnichenko lead the way with a  new personal best and 11th place overall finish.  Rounding out the scoring  for the JV team was J.D. Fye, Kevin McDougal, Nick Marsh, and Nick DiGiulio.",
