    "categories": [
      "Boys Meet Results",
      "Honors"
    ],
    "gender": "boys",
    "body": "Congratulations to  senior Andrew Klecan in his  [state  runner-up  finish in the pole vault](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sJcVH2RNMZ8) at the 100th State Championship of Ohio.   He set yet another school  record with a vault of 15 feet to earn his All-Ohio status.  In the  4x800  relay, the team of Corwin Swint, J.D. Horton, Ty Griffin, and Josh  Tormasi  finished 7th overall with a 7:53.35 to earn All-Ohio status.  Full  results  can be found [here](http://www.baumspage.com/ohsaa/tf/2007/bd1.htm)",
