    "gender": "boys",
    "body": "In Boy's Track action last night at the Regional Championships, Andrew  Klecan  won the Regional Pole Vault Championship with a vault of  [14 feet  6 inches](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mIGID7_I3cY) and  the 4 x 800m relay team set another school record, running  [7:49.94  and finishing  2nd](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8pweVMd_SXc).  Both Andrew Klecan and the 4 x 800m relay team of Corwin  Swint, J.D.  Horton, Josh Tormasi, and Ty Griffin have now qualified for next weeks  State  Meet.  Also qualifying for Friday's finals was the 4 x 400m relay team  of John  Clark, Trevor Biddle, Corwin Swint, and Ty Griffin.",
