    "title": "Ty Griffin and Josh Tormasi two of many athletes qualify to Regional Championship",
    "categories": [
      "Boys Meet Results",
      "Honors"
    ],
    "gender": "boys",
    "body": "In Boy's Track Action  Friday Night at the District Meet, Ty  Griffin and Josh Tormasi won their respected events and claimed  Individual  District Titles. Ty in the 1600m and   [Josh  in 3200m](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vaf-t8E5HW8).  Josh's time of 9:25.40 broke his own school record,  district record and stadium record.   Josh also finished 2nd in the 1600m.  Other's having outstanding days  and  qualifying for regionals on the day were: Dan Harsh 3rd in High Jump,  Andrew  Klecan 3rd in Pole Vault, Rob Dugan 3rd in the 100m, J.D. Horton 3rd in  the  3200m, Kyle Hug 4th in Discus, Corwin Swint, John Clark, Trevor Biddle,  and Ty  Griffin 3rd in the 4 x 400m Relay, and Corwin Swint, J.D. Horton, Josh  Tormasi,  and Ty Griffin 1st in the 4 x 800m Relay.\n\nBe sure to check out the [media page](http://perrylocal.org/track/media/) to  see some of the races.",
